    "title": "Kimi \"Interstellar Program\": Build AGI with Us",
    "preview_text": "Kimi was founded three years ago to push AGI forward. Last year, we released an open-source trillion-parameter agentic model, extending AI capabilities from conversation to action.\n \nToday, we're a",
    "cover_url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HE_MslaaEAAdQTH.jpg",
    "content_state": {
      "blocks": [
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "826r",
          "text": "Kimi was founded three years ago to push AGI forward. Last year, we released an open-source trillion-parameter agentic model, extending AI capabilities from conversation to action.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 0,
              "length": 1,
              "offset": 0
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "63gui",
          "text": " ",
          "type": "atomic"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "6ctgs",
          "text": "Today, we're a team of 300 exceptional people working closely together to scale toward AGI. ",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "7maan",
          "text": "We need more builders to join us and accelerate this work.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 22,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "eutol",
          "text": "Who We're Looking For:",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "dgnfo",
          "text": "Researchers, engineers, founders, product developers, if you're among the best in your field, we want you.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "fnjom",
          "text": "Here, there are no limits on compute, scope, or approach. You'll work hands-on with other builders to create our most capable models.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 28,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "bh3b0",
          "text": "Scale the Journey with Kimi:",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "89bul",
          "text": "Whether you're already with us or about to join, you can earn a full-time offer through the Interstellar Program. ",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "dimnd",
          "text": "Spend 3–6 months here, show us what you can do, pass the review, and we'll extend a formal offer. Your graduation year doesn't matter, your impact does.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "8rtvr",
          "text": "Your options will be granted at the 2026 valuation when you begin your internship, with vesting starting immediately. When you officially join full-time after graduation, the value of your equity will grow alongside the progress we create.",
          "type": "blockquote"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "39fvo",
          "text": "Today, we invite you to join Kimi in pushing forward on AGI, and  grow through the journey together.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 13,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "5gl8v",
          "text": "How to Apply:",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 1,
              "length": 18,
              "offset": 6
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "7qc9n",
          "text": "Email talent@moonshot.ai with subject: [Interstellar Program] + Name + Position",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "2l9r4",
          "text": "Ask a Kimi employee for a referral",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        }
      ],
